org.apache.paimon.reader

Interface FileRecordIterator<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of the record.
    All Superinterfaces:
    RecordReader.RecordIterator<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ApplyDeletionFileRecordIterator, ColumnarRowIterator, IteratorResultIterator

    public interface FileRecordIterator<T>
extends RecordReader.RecordIterator<T>
    Wrap RecordReader.RecordIterator to support returning the record's row position and file Path.
